description: I’ve never had the pleasure of touring a home like this one before! If you are in search of top A-rated schools, check out the schools this house is zoned to!! If you like walking your child to school, RAE is just on the other side of the walking path. Family room W/vaulted ceilings, built in shelving, direct vent gas fireplace surrounded by a designer mantle w/corbels & shiplap accent wall above. Kitchen has ample space for storage & counter space for prep & cooking, w/raised dishwasher & gas cooktop, Kohler silgranite sink & professional style faucet. All bathrooms have been updated to the NINES, including the powder bath! Handscraped hardwood flooring upstairs & down. ALL windows have been replaced w/energy efficient double paned, low-e windows, Motorized gate w/keypad for pedestrian gate. BOTH HVAC systems (coils & condensers) AND furnaces have been replaced. Huge pool w/oversized spa, all w/pebble-tec surfaces, 6 feet deep at the deepest point. SO MUCH MORE! Come see it in person!
